{"tid":2278283,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一年前 有個人走出黎話中共係美國建國以來最強大既對手 當時冇人信佢","createTime":"2020-11-09T05:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T06:59:33.000Z","uid":73381,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c86b87cc18f2bd1b399e158265b30a6820482c","tid":2278283,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:00:55.000Z","msg":"同不同意中共係美國建國以來最強大既對手？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740712</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n事實證明<br />\n無論係鼠疫 豬瘟 水災 蝗災 武漢肺炎 貿易戰<br />\n（漏咗請補充）上面每一單連登仔都吹到滅國咁濟<br />\n但中國仍然好似咩事都冇 中共既政權完全固若金湯<br />\n相反美國就黎自己收自己皮<br />\n<br />\n唔知連登仔今時今日係咪仲咁低估中共呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc57afe5cb6e4ad2a86109572a7e0af8622f4ea","tid":2278283,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:01:19.000Z","msg":"講到共產黨 冇人清楚得過原post樓主<br />\n啲傻仔唔岩聽就比負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實你地真係唔太了解共產黨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2089971\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2089971</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2d94a3c5353c6dd49127afd9e8b5ed2f310e006a","tid":2278283,"uid":379666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0694f61a735ffe7220fc18a99382d45a1d2146","tid":2278283,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:01:39.000Z","msg":"走得太前 通常都冇咩好結果🚬"},{"pid":"3149e0384387fa8553929c6acd2eb4326484f65a","tid":2278283,"uid":311626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:02:59.000Z","msg":"連登講將來既野會被人負評的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991fd88b80af833f07034083f1705ddcc31ec83d","tid":2278283,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:03:2